</section>
</div>
<div class="hidden-content control-hide">
<p class="ql-align-center"> 而泼洒出的色彩大小形状、</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">颜色轨迹及泼洒深浅度，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">都可从侧面体现出儿童或内向谨慎，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">或外向活泼的性格。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">每个儿童对于不同色彩的偏爱，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">也使得每幅画面基调有所不同。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20200330/95f9a9f9a3f54e4d95caa86475d2ad43.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>1、泼墨创作作品</strong></p>
