<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200730/6d7125483eb44f168d57796535af3451.jpeg" max-width="600"><span class="img-desc" style="font-size: 16px;">▲寸草春晖主题美育——王笑楚</span></img></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200730/6d53112543e6472fa9cb4335b22b41ac.jpeg" max-width="600"><span class="img-desc" style="font-size: 16px;">▲寸草春晖主题美育——贾聿辰</span></img></p>
